**Flutter Firebase Uygulama Şablonu (Japonca Kaynak)**

Hukusuke'nin Flutter + Firebase başlangıç kiti. Clean Architecture, Riverpod state management ve Firestore CRUD işlemleri için production-ready yapı.

**Kurulum:**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/hukusuke1007/flutter_app_template
cd flutter_app_template
flutter pub get
# FlutterFire CLI ile Firebase bağla:
dart pub global activate flutterfire_cli
flutterfire configure
flutter run
```

**Riverpod + Firestore Provider:**
```dart
// lib/features/todo/data/todo_repository.dart
class TodoRepository {
  final FirebaseFirestore _firestore;
  TodoRepository(this._firestore);

  Stream<List<Todo>> watchTodos(String userId) {
    return _firestore
        .collection('users').doc(userId)
        .collection('todos')
        .orderBy('createdAt', descending: true)
        .snapshots()
        .map((s) => s.docs.map(Todo.fromFirestore).toList());
  }

  Future<void> addTodo(String userId, String title) =>
    _firestore.collection('users').doc(userId)
      .collection('todos').add({
        'title': title, 'done': false,
        'createdAt': FieldValue.serverTimestamp()
      });
}

final todoRepoProvider = Provider((ref) =>
  TodoRepository(FirebaseFirestore.instance));
```

**Özellikler:** Feature-first mimari, GoRouter navigasyon, Firebase Analytics, Crashlytics, Remote Config.

