## Cloudflare + Firebase Starter Kit

Cloudflare Workers/Pages ile Firebase'i birleştiren edge-first uygulama başlangıç kiti.

**Mimari:**
```
Kullanıcı → Cloudflare CDN (edge) → Firebase
         → Workers (serverless) → Firestore
         → Pages (static host) → Firebase Auth
```

**Cloudflare Worker + Firebase Admin:**
```javascript
// worker.js (Cloudflare Workers)
import { initializeApp, cert } from 'firebase-admin/app';
import { getFirestore } from 'firebase-admin/firestore';

const app = initializeApp({
  credential: cert({
    projectId: FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID,
    privateKey: FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY.replace(/\\n/g, '\n'),
    clientEmail: FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL
  })
});

export default {
  async fetch(request, env) {
    const db = getFirestore();
    const snapshot = await db.collection('products').get();
    const products = snapshot.docs.map(d => ({id: d.id, ...d.data()}));
    return Response.json({ products });
  }
};
```

